casebody.head_matter:
Salvatore J. MORETTI, Petitioner
v.
BERGEN COUNTY PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE
No. 19-5284
Supreme Court of the United States.
October 7, 2019
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of New Jersey, Appellate Division dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice Alito took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
